CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 17, 1970, pg. 6, reads: "Church Leaders Celebrate - The exclusive dining area at the Top of The Towers was the scene of the Pre Christmas Dinner Party given by the Baptist Ministers and their wives recently... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Man, and woman, possibly Mrs. Bowick, standing at microphone, at Baptist Ministers pre-Christmas dinner, Top of the Towers restaurant
